Package: digiRhythm
Type: Package
Title: Analyzing animal's rhythmicity
Version: 0.0.0.9000
Authors@R: 
    person(given = "Hassan (Roland)",
           family = "Nasser",
           role = c("aut", "cre"),
           email = "hassan.nasser@me.com",
           comment = c(ORCID = "0000-0003-1821-3234"))
Maintainer: Roland-Hassan Nasser <roland.nasser@agroscope.admin.c>
Description: digiRhythm is an R library developed at Agroscope and provides 
    a set of tools to analyze and visualize the rhythmic behavior of animals.
    The main functionalities of this library are: computing the degree of functional
    coupling, visualizing actograms, clustering day-animal activities and more.
